        <div class="container">
            <div class="section__header">
                <h2>About Us</h2>
                <p>Founded in 2024, TalentQuery is committed to connecting exceptional talent with visionary companies.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                    <p>Our strength comes from the minds and hearts of our team, each of them providing their talents, experience, vision, and dreams.</p>
                    <h3 class="mt-4">What we value</h3>
                    <div class="feature">
                        <div class="feature__icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-award"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="feature__title">Quality</h4>
                        <p class="feature__text">Commitment to delivering the highest standards in every aspect of our service.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature">
                        <div class="feature__icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="feature__title">Collaboration</h4>
                        <p class="feature__text">Fostering teamwork and partnership, we believe in achieving more together.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                    <div class="feature">
                        <div class="feature__icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="feature__title">Transparency</h4>
                        <p class="feature__text">Maintaining open and honest communication, building trust every step of the way.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature">
                        <div class="feature__icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                        </div>
