                    </div>
                    <div class="feature">
                        <div class="feature__icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="feature__title">Regulatory Compliance</h4>
                        <p class="feature__text">We manage labor aspects in each country.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature">
                        <div class="feature__icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="feature__title">Easy Termination or Extension</h4>
                        <p class="feature__text">Agile processes to modify or terminate contracts according to your goals.</p>
                    </div>
